{
  "npc": {
    "id": "npc.aldo",
    "name": "Aldo",
    "role": "mentor",
    "shortDescription": "守灯人。脸上有大片伤疤，左手少了两根手指。再不下水。",
    "dialogRoot": {
      "id": "aldo.root",
      "text": "黎明前的鸢尾湾。雾还没散。Aldo 坐在长椅上，看着海。他没回头。\n\n「准备好了？」",
      "choices": [
        {
          "id": "ready",
          "label": "准备好了。",
          "next": "aldo.briefing",
          "visibleIf": { "kind": "notHasFlag", "flag": "flag.tutorial_complete" }
        },
        {
          "id": "not_yet",
          "label": "还差一点。",
          "next": "aldo.look_around",
          "visibleIf": { "kind": "notHasFlag", "flag": "flag.tutorial_complete" }
        },
        {
          "id": "morning",
          "label": "（坐下，跟他看一会儿海）",
          "next": "aldo.harbor_morning",
          "visibleIf": { "kind": "hasFlag", "flag": "flag.tutorial_complete" }
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  "dialogs": {
    "aldo.briefing": {
      "id": "aldo.briefing",
      "text": "「让我看看你的装备。」\n\nAldo 接过去，挨个检查。\n\n「你导师的装备，我帮你保养了这么多年。今天你去东礁那个老沉船下去走一趟，能带回来的都带回来。算是你在这片海的初次潜水，简单。」\n\n他停顿了一下。\n\n「记住：氧气是时间，氮气是债。慢慢上来，别贪。」\n\n「四样东西你要盯紧——体力，氧气，理智，氮气。前两样你能直接看到。第三样你自己感觉。第四样会找你算账。」",
      "choices": [
        {
          "id": "depart_east",
          "label": "出海到东礁（初次潜水）。",
          "next": "end",
          "visibleIf": { "kind": "notHasFlag", "flag": "flag.tutorial_complete" },
          "effects": [
            { "kind": "setFlag", "flag": "flag.tutorial_briefed" },
            { "kind": "startDive", "zoneId": "zone.east_reef" }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "open_chart",
          "label": "（摊开海图，挑一个潜点）",
          "next": "end",
          "visibleIf": { "kind": "hasFlag", "flag": "flag.tutorial_complete" },
          "effects": [
            { "kind": "openChart" }
          ],
          "filler": true
        },
        {
          "id": "ask_mentor",
          "label": "你认识我导师？",
          "next": "aldo.about_mentor"
        }
      ]
    },
    "aldo.harbor_morning": {
      "id": "aldo.harbor_morning",
      "text": "你在长椅另一头坐下。海面有风，雾往外退。\n\n「潮位正好。」Aldo 朝海图桌那边抬了抬下巴，「今天去哪，你自己挑——那些坐标，你现在比我熟。」\n\n他顿了顿。\n\n「带够气。回来吃饭。」",
      "choices": [
        {
          "id": "coords_left",
          "label": "还剩几处坐标。",
          "next": "aldo.coords_left",
          "visibleIf": {
            "kind": "any",
            "of": [
              { "kind": "notHasFlag", "flag": "story.ch1.anchor.reef" },
              { "kind": "notHasFlag", "flag": "story.ch1.anchor.wreck" },
              { "kind": "notHasFlag", "flag": "story.ch1.anchor.midwater" },
              { "kind": "notHasFlag", "flag": "story.ch1.anchor.vent" }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "open_chart",
          "label": "（摊开海图，挑一个潜点）",
          "next": "end",
          "effects": [
            { "kind": "openChart" }
          ],
          "filler": true
        },
        {
          "id": "ask_mentor",
          "label": "你认识我导师？",
          "next": "aldo.about_mentor"
        },
        {
          "id": "ask_tides",
          "label": "潮汐有讲究？",
          "next": "aldo.tide_intel",
          "visibleIf": { "kind": "notHasFlag", "flag": "intel.aldo.lunar_tides" }
        },
        {
          "id": "voss_recall",
          "label": "（问他，从前有没有一个打听章鱼的人）",
          "next": "aldo.voss_recall",
          "visibleIf": {
            "kind": "all",
            "of": [
              { "kind": "hasFlag", "flag": "flag.voss.recording_heard" },
              { "kind": "notHasFlag", "flag": "flag.aldo.voss_seen" }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "leave",
          "label": "（再坐一会儿，然后起身）",
          "next": "end"
        }
      ]
    },
    "aldo.voss_recall": {
      "id": "aldo.voss_recall",
      "text": "Aldo 没马上答。\n\n「见过一个。好些年前。」他望着海，「一个人来的，话少。眼睛跟称秤似的，把你也称进去。」\n\n他顿了顿。「满口问章鱼——哪儿有，什么时候出。我说这片水里没那东西。他不争，只看着你——像没弄明白的是你。」",
      "onEnter": [
        { "kind": "setFlag", "flag": "flag.aldo.voss_seen" }
      ],
      "choices": [
        { "id": "back", "label": "（记下）", "next": "aldo.harbor_morning" }
      ]
    },
    "aldo.about_mentor": {
      "id": "aldo.about_mentor",
      "text": "Aldo 沉默了很久。\n\n「他是上一代最后一个还敢去深处的人。」\n\n他没说更多。",
      "choices": [
        {
          "id": "to_sites",
          "label": "（跟他提你找到的那些样地）",
          "next": "aldo.mentor.sites",
          "visibleIf": {
            "kind": "all",
            "of": [
              {
                "kind": "any",
                "of": [
                  { "kind": "hasFlag", "flag": "story.ch1.anchor.reef" },
                  { "kind": "hasFlag", "flag": "story.ch1.anchor.wreck" },
                  { "kind": "hasFlag", "flag": "story.ch1.anchor.midwater" },
                  { "kind": "hasFlag", "flag": "story.ch1.anchor.vent" }
                ]
              },
              { "kind": "notHasFlag", "flag": "flag.aldo.sites_seen" }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "to_guilt",
          "label": "（他像有话要说——等他开口）",
          "next": "aldo.mentor.guilt",
          "visibleIf": {
            "kind": "all",
            "of": [
              { "kind": "hasFlag", "flag": "story.ch1.anchor.reef" },
              { "kind": "hasFlag", "flag": "story.ch1.anchor.wreck" },
              { "kind": "hasFlag", "flag": "story.ch1.anchor.midwater" },
              { "kind": "notHasFlag", "flag": "flag.aldo.guilt_seen" }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "back",
          "label": "（沉默地点头）",
          "next": "aldo.briefing",
          "visibleIf": { "kind": "notHasFlag", "flag": "flag.tutorial_complete" }
        },
        {
          "id": "back_morning",
          "label": "（沉默地点头）",
          "next": "aldo.harbor_morning",
          "visibleIf": { "kind": "hasFlag", "flag": "flag.tutorial_complete" }
        }
      ]
    },
    "aldo.look_around": {
      "id": "aldo.look_around",
      "text": "「随你。但太阳一出，潮位就涨。」\n\n你在港口走了一圈。气瓶师 Otto 在仓库门口给一只气瓶上压力，没抬头。打捞商 Mira 的柜台已经开了——可以去找她出手东西。海鸥在桅杆上叫。\n\n回到长椅时，Aldo 还在那个位置。",
      "choices": [
        {
          "id": "now_ready",
          "label": "现在准备好了。",
          "next": "aldo.briefing"
        }
      ]
    },
    "aldo.mentor.sites": {
      "id": "aldo.mentor.sites",
      "text": "你说出第一处样地的位置，他听着，没打断。\n等你说完，他才开口：「那几个漆号是他教你认的。一横两点，背流那侧。」他顿了顿，「你还记得。」\n他没夸你。可他往海那边看的时候，绷了十年的肩，松了一点。",
      "onEnter": [
        { "kind": "setFlag", "flag": "flag.aldo.sites_seen" }
      ],
      "choices": [
        { "id": "back", "label": "（点头）", "next": "aldo.harbor_morning" }
      ]
    },
    "aldo.mentor.guilt": {
      "id": "aldo.mentor.guilt",
      "text": "他先开的口。\n「那天你没上船。」不是问句。「我知道。装备是你来取的——晚了半天。」\n你没说话。十年了，第一次有人替你把这句说出来。\n「他选的人是你。你没上去，不是你的错。是海。」他看着海，「海不挑人，也不还人。」\n他停了很久。「可你现在要去把他找回来。我不拦了。把气带够。」",
      "onEnter": [
        { "kind": "setFlag", "flag": "flag.aldo.guilt_seen" }
      ],
      "choices": [
        { "id": "back", "label": "（沉默地点头）", "next": "aldo.harbor_morning" }
      ]
    },
    "aldo.coords_left": {
      "id": "aldo.coords_left",
      "text": "「日志上四个坐标，你去过几个心里有数。」他朝海图桌抬下巴，「剩下的，趁你还想去，去。别一口气贪到底。」",
      "choices": [
        {
          "id": "open_chart",
          "label": "（摊开海图，挑一个潜点）",
          "next": "end",
          "effects": [
            { "kind": "openChart" }
          ],
          "filler": true
        },
        { "id": "back", "label": "（点头）", "next": "aldo.harbor_morning" }
      ]
    },
    "aldo.tide_intel": {
      "id": "aldo.tide_intel",
      "text": "「月亮拉着海走。到了朔——新月那几天——大潮退得最狠。」\n\n他朝东礁那边偏了下头。\n\n「东礁外有片浅滩，平日没在水里，看不出。大潮退到底，礁盘露出来，那会儿才下得去。错过了，就等下一个朔。」\n\n「记着潮历。该等的时候，就等——海不催你，可它也不等你。」",
      "onEnter": [
        { "kind": "setFlag", "flag": "intel.aldo.lunar_tides" }
      ],
      "choices": [
        { "id": "back", "label": "（记下了）", "next": "aldo.harbor_morning" }
      ]
    }
  }
}
